
## RDS (Relational Database Service)
--> A database structure to recognize relations between stored items of information
--  Two types of backups
--> Automated Backups
--> DB Snapshots
 
 ## Elastic Container Service (ECS)
 --> Highly scalable, fast , container management Service
 --> Easy to run, stop and manage Docker containers on a cluster
 --> Cluster on a serverless infrastructure
## Architecture of Amazom ECS
--> Container Image:
--> Container registry(ECR)
--> Amazon ECS

-->Task are launched using the Fargate
  task has 2 components:
  ECS container instance
  container agent

--> Cluster is set of ECS container
--> handles scheduling, monitoring and scaling requests